title: 820-00165 No 3V3_S5
message: This board had some minor liquid-damage. Had to replace R7080 to restore 3V42 and MagSafe light. It has no PP3V3_S5. It has 3V42, 3.4V on SMC_PM_G2_EN. 8.59V on PPBUS. Not sure where to go next.
